                    <h1>How To Arrange Step By Step ?</h1>
                    <p>
                        Start with the second element: Consider the first element as already sorted.
                        <br />Iterate through the remaining elements:
                        <br /> Pick the next unsorted element.
                        <br /> Compare it with the elements to its left that are already sorted.
                        <br /> "Walk" it back to its correct position by shifting larger elements to the right until it finds its place.
                        <br /> Repeat for all elements: Continue this process until all elements are in their correct positions, resulting in a sorted list.
                    </p>

